∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (U : Set ℂ) (hU : IsSimplyConnected U)
  (f : ℂ → E) (h : ∀ z ∈ U, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) (γ : ℂ → ℂ) (hγ : Continuous γ) (hγ' : γ 0 = γ 1)
  (hγ'' : ∀ t, γ t ∈ U), (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (hU : IsSimplyConnected U)
  {f : ℂ → E} (hf : ∀ z ∈ U, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) {γ : Path ℂ},
  γ ∈ LoopsIn U → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (hU : IsSimplyConnected U)
  {f : ℂ → E} (h : ∀ z ∈ U, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) {γ : ℂ → ℂ} (hγ : Continuous γ) (hγ' : γ 0 = γ 1)
  (hγ'' : ∀ t, γ t ∈ U), (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (D : Set ℂ) (hD : IsSimplyConnected D)
  (f : ℂ → E) (hf : ∀ z ∈ D, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) (γ : Path ℂ), γ.IsClosed ∧ γ.mapsTo D → γ.lineIntegral f = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (hU : IsSimplyConnected U)
  {f : ℂ → E} (hf : HolomorphicOn f U) {γ : ℂ → ℂ} (hγ : Continuous γ) (hγ' : ∀ t, γ t ∈ U) (hγ_closed : γ 0 = γ 1),
  ∮ (z : ℂ) in path γ 0 1, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} {γ : ℂ → ℂ},
  IsSimplyConnected U →
    (∀ z ∈ U, DifferentiableAt ℂ γ z) →
    MeasureTheory.MeasureTheory.ClosedCurve γ →
    (∮ (z : ℂ) in C(γ, U), γ z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (γ : ℂ → ℂ)
  [inst_2 : IsSimplyConnected U], IsClosed γ → (∀ z ∈ U, DifferentiableAt ℂ γ z) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, γ z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ),
  IsSimplyConnected U →
    ContinuousOn f U →
      HolomorphicOn ℂ f U →
        ContinuousOn γ (Set.Icc 0 1) →
          γ '' Set.Icc 0 1 ⊆ U →
            γ 0 = γ 1 → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {U : Set ℂ} (f : ℂ → E),
  IsSimplyConnected U → HolomorphicOn f U →
    ∀ (γ : ℂ → ℂ) (hγ : Continuous γ) (hγ' : γ 0 = γ 1) (hγ_range : Set.Range γ ⊆ U),
    (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0
